reviews.text:
Awesome food especially the western set meal! Even the side dish such as the ice lemon tea, mushroom soup, french fries and salad taste good. For $9.90 nett it is really cheap.

Dining environment is cosy - good music, peaceful and clean. Staff are polite.

This place is a hidden gem.

Lots of parking lots in Joo Chiat Complex.
Love the fresh oysters! Reasonable drinks. Other basic snacks were good too!

Nice place to chill at, maybe even hold small meetings etc. It's a KTV bar/ cafe, the alcohol selection is okay, there's no draft beers just bottled and cans...there's hard liquor (I think?).

Food is decent at best, not that it's horrible but the taste just doesn't stand out. I would consider it slightly overpriced because the portion is way too little but again, it isn't very expensive.

Would I recommend eating there? No.

Would I recommend drinking there? Probably but it won't be my top few choices when I think about places to drink.

Standard drop! Not a good place for night hang out now.
Shop closed, forget abt visiting.

Brilliant and comfy. Great food. Large portions.  I love this place.
DOWNGRADED TO 1 STAR RATING.
